---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import { site, mailLink } from '../data/site';

const a = site.address;
---

<Layout
  current="/cookie-policy"
  title="Cookie Policy - Kensons Garage | Car Body Repair South London"
  description="How Kensons Garage uses cookies. We set no tracking cookies by default — only essential cookies and a local consent preference."
  noindex={true}
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="Legal"
    title="Cookie Policy"
    crumb="Cookie Policy"
  />

  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="legal-prose fade-in">
        <p><strong>Last updated: June 2026</strong></p>

        <p>
          This Cookie Policy explains how {site.name} uses cookies and similar technologies on this
          website. It should be read alongside our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>What are cookies?</h2>
        <p>
          Cookies are small text files that a website can place on your device when you visit. They are
          widely used to make websites work, to remember your preferences and, on some sites, to gather
          information about how the site is used. Similar technologies — such as your browser's
          <strong>localStorage</strong> — can store small amounts of information in your browser in the
          same way.
        </p>

        <h2>We set no tracking cookies by default</h2>
        <p>
          This is a static website, and it sets <strong>no tracking or advertising cookies by default</strong>.
          We do not profile you, and we do not share your browsing behaviour with advertisers.
        </p>

        <h2>The cookies and storage we do use</h2>
        <h3>Essential</h3>
        <p>
          A small number of essential items may be needed for the site to function correctly and to
          remember the choices you make. In particular, when you respond to our cookie notice we store a
          single <strong>local consent preference</strong> in your browser's localStorage so that we do not
          show you the banner again. This is <strong>not a tracking cookie</strong> — it never leaves your
          device, contains no personal information, and is used only to remember your choice. Essential
          storage like this does not require your consent under the law.
        </p>
        <h3>Analytics (optional)</h3>
        <p>
          We may, only <strong>with your consent</strong>, use privacy-respecting analytics to understand
          how the site is used so we can improve it. These are not enabled unless you choose "Accept" on our
          cookie notice, and you can change your mind at any time (see below). If you select "Reject", no
          analytics are used.
        </p>

        <h2>Third-party cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Some content embedded from third parties may set its own cookies if you choose to interact with it:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Google Maps</strong> — the embedded map on our contact page may set cookies from Google
            when it loads. These are controlled by Google under its own cookie and privacy policies.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>WhatsApp</strong> — if you click through to message us on WhatsApp, WhatsApp may set its
            own cookies under its own policies.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We do not control these third-party cookies. Please refer to the relevant provider's own cookie
          policy for details.
        </p>

        <h2>How to control cookies</h2>
        <p>
          You are always in control. You can:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Use our cookie notice to accept or reject optional analytics;</li>
          <li>
            Manage or delete cookies and clear stored site data directly in your browser settings — most
            browsers let you block all cookies, delete existing ones, or be warned before a cookie is set;
          </li>
          <li>Clear your browser's localStorage, which will remove the local consent preference described above.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          To learn more about cookies and how to manage them, you can visit
          <a href="https://ico.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ico.org.uk</a>. Please note that
          blocking essential storage may affect how parts of the site behave.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this Cookie Policy, please contact us:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>{site.name}</strong></li>
          <li>{a.unit}, {a.street}, {a.area}, {a.city} {a.postcode}</li>
          <li>Email: <a href={mailLink}>{site.email}</a></li>
          <li>Telephone: {site.phoneMobile} or {site.phoneSecondary}</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
